"{\"uid\": \"sandiegouniontribune.com-news-nation-world-story-2024-02-28-paris-city-hall-says-no-olympic-games-policing-plans-were-lost-in-theft-of-a-workers-computer-gear\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"e-Edition  Get the latest news in your inbox!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the latest news in your inbox!\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 83, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"e-Edition  Trending:  PARISPARIS\\u00a0-\\u00a0Paris City Hall said Wednesday that no policing plans forthe upcoming Olympic Gameswere lost in the theft of computer gear reported by one of its employees.\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A City Hall statement said: \\\"Initial checks established that the worker did not possess any information relating to the organization and deployment of law enforcement during the Olympic and Paralympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French broadcaster BFMTV first reported Tuesday evening that a computer and USB keys containing Olympic Games security plans for Paris City Hall were stolen aboard a train at the French capital's Gare du Nord station.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9599173576409138, \"rank\": 0.04155265875619727, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.9985514973704287, \"rank\": 0.0014505914288463553, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9599173576409138, \"rank\": 0.04155265875619727, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BFM said one of the USB keys was encrypted and stored security plans relating to roads and traffic for the July 26-Aug. 11 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 0.9987267499588985, \"rank\": 0.0011462136975218514, \"text\": \"BFM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.9985514973704287, \"rank\": 0.0014505914288463553, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ina city repeatedly hit by deadly extremist attacks, security isthe biggest challengefor Paris Games organizers.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutor's office on Wednesday described media coverage of the theft as \\\"hasty.\\\"\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994822701, \"rank\": 5.177357011944328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said a City Hall engineer had lost a bag at Gare du Nord on Monday and reported that it contained a USB key used for work.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\", \"score\": 0.968966609654763, \"rank\": 0.02028736815278697, \"text\": \"City Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.9985514973704287, \"rank\": 0.0014505914288463553, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, it is important to specify that this key only contained notes related to traffic in Paris during the Olympic Games, and not on sensitive security plans,\\\" the prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994822701, \"rank\": 5.177357011944328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"City Hall's statement said the worker's computer gear \\\"contained notes for internal use,\\\" concerning the employee's IT-related work for the Paris traffic department.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\", \"score\": 0.968966609654763, \"rank\": 0.02028736815278697, \"text\": \"City Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994822701, \"rank\": 5.177357011944328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said an investigation is underway into the \\\"proven breaches of internal security procedures\\\" and that depending on its findings, \\\"sanctions will be taken.\\\"\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP coverage of the Paris Olympics:https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9996633480914549, \"rank\": 0.00033666646583748334, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\"}]}]}"